\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
2.) High-Level Premise: Basically, something like a "post-war", similar to Fallout. It'll be Sci-Fi like Encased and/or Colony Ship. It won't be Fantasy (because I actually hate Fantasy). However, there is a lot that I really like about Baldur's Gate 3, and I'll be borrowing various things from that game.}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
3.) Setting: One big city, yes. Specifically, in the city of Concordia, which is a future "robot/human Sci-Fi update" of what we currently know today as Concordia Station (which is a real place. You can look it up if you'd like). Concordia, due to its geographical setting, ended up being the most populous surviving city in post-war Antarctica.}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
4.) Core Fantasy: definitely moral choices and consequences, absolutely. There will be some tactical combat, though meaningful choices with real-world consequences will drive the core of the story}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
5.) Party Size: I'm thinking just one companion at a time.}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
6.) Combat Preference: isometric grid-based tactical like Fallouts 1 and 2, Wasteland 3, Baldur's Gate 3, etc etc and so on}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
7.) Any must-have systems: absolutely branching dialogue, absolutely skill checks, absolutely a reputation system. A camera system like in Baldur's Gate 3. There will definitely be an inventory system. I haven't quite made up my mind about crafting, although I am open to the idea.}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
So far as what kind of world we're stepping into, basically, it's something vaguely like "Fallout New Vegas meets Cyberpunk, in Antarctica, with robots and humans"}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Thought for 6s}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Perfect \u8212\'97 thank you for the detailed lore dump. "Inner Tepenia" sounds like a rich, atmospheric sci-fi CRPG: post-Midnight War survival in a frozen, cyberpunk-infused Antarctic megacity where robots and humans coexist uneasily under the long shadow of the Falkland Treaty and Amundsen Tower. Concordia as the last major hub, with moral gray areas everywhere, reputation shaping alliances, skill checks for hacking/tech/survival/diplomacy, and tactical grid combat. One companion at a time keeps it focused and intimate \u8212\'97 excellent for your writing strengths.This vibe is Fallout New Vegas \u215\'d7 Cyberpunk 2077 \u215\'d7 Encased, but grounded in harsh Antarctic isolation. I love it.Core Game Pillars We'll Build (Tailored to Your Vision)}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af6 \ltrch\hich\af6\loch\f6\dbch\af6 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls10 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Exploration: Isometric grid-based movement in a dense, multi-level Concordia (snow-covered domes, retro-fitted research towers, underground sectors, neon-lit robot districts).}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af6 \ltrch\hich\af6\loch\f6\dbch\af6 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls10 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Dialogue & Choices: Deep branching conversations with your prose, skill checks (e.g., "Persuasion", "Robotics", "Survival", "Hacking"), and lasting reputation/faction effects.}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af6 \ltrch\hich\af6\loch\f6\dbch\af6 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls10 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
