one important thing to keep in mind is that, while Concordia is part of the Janbogo Subnet (which is a regional division of the greater Antarctican internet, or Arcanet), Janbogo itself is a separate city. It's a future Sci-Fi updating of what we currently know today as Jang Bogo Station. If you'd like, I recommend reading up about it. It's really quite interesting. In any case, the Central Hub and the Undergrid would be part of Concordia (which is where the game takes place) as opposed to Janbogo (which would be inaccessible within the context of the game, as the game only occupies that one city of Concordia)}
