Excellent question. This is exactly the kind of thing that can break immersion, so we need strong, believable, multi-layered reasons why \u8220\'93just fix the energy grid\u8221\'94 is never a simple or complete solution.Here\u8217\'92s a rich set of internally consistent explanations rooted in your world:1. Fundamental Structural Damage (The \u8220\'93Wounded Core\u8221\'94 Problem)}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af6 \ltrch\hich\af6\loch\f6\dbch\af6 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls242 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
