\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af6 \ltrch\hich\af6\loch\f6\dbch\af6 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls242 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Any attempt to \u8220\'93fully repair\u8221\'94 it requires shutting down large sections for months, which would trigger immediate city-wide blackouts far worse than the current rolling failures.}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af6 \ltrch\hich\af6\loch\f6\dbch\af6 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls242 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
The core is now a patchwork of pre-war, wartime, and post-evacuation technology that are incompatible. Forcing a full repair risks a catastrophic cascade failure (meltdown or total freeze).}
