\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af6 \ltrch\hich\af6\loch\f6\dbch\af6 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls247 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
There are micro-fractures and corrupted control AIs running throughout the entire grid. Fixing surface problems often awakens deeper, more dangerous failures.}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af6 \ltrch\hich\af6\loch\f6\dbch\af6 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls247 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Parts of the grid have become semi-sentient or corrupted by Arcanet data bleed \u8212\'97 \u8220\'93fixing\u8221\'94 them risks creating rogue subsystems.}
\par \pard\plain \s18\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af6 \ltrch\hich\af6\loch\f6\dbch\af6 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls247 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
